nsation at Huron Consulting Group, which includes a combination of pay, stock and equity, and benefits. Overall, 6 Participants rate their compensation at Huron Consulting Group a C, or 69 out of 100.Overall, employees at Huron Consulting Group are extremely happy with their team.  Participants grade the quality of their coworkers an A. The Majority believe the meetings at Huron Consulting Group are effective, and the majority look forward to interacting with their coworkers.The majority of employees at Huron Consulting Group believe the environment at Huron Consulting Group is positive. Most Participants believe the pace of work at Huron Consulting Group is comfortably fast. Overall, the employees at Huron Consulting Group are extremely happy, based on their aggregated ratings of future outlook, customer perception, and their excitement going to work. The 6 employees who participated believe the future outlook of Huron Consulting Group is positive.
